            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1280230</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[
<p>电影《28 Years Later》稍早前发布首部预告片，电影标榜全程使用 iPhone 15 Pro Max 拍摄，展示智能手机在专业电影制作领域的潜力。电影将于 2025 年 6 月 20 日在美国上映，为观众带来耳目一新的惊吓体验。</p><p><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="28 YEARS LATER – Official Trailer (HD)" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/mcvLKldPM08?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></p><p>《28 Years Later》是 2002 年上映的经典英国灾难片《28 Days Later》之续集，据外媒报道，《28 Years Later》整部电影全程以 iPhone 15 Pro Max 拍摄，为影片增添了独特的视觉风格。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280445" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/bgus_2970142_012-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/bgus_2970142_012-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/bgus_2970142_012.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Jodie Comer 在《28 Years Later》片场，外媒指右边的摄录系统为 iPhone 15 Pro Max<br />图片来源：<a href="https://www.wired.com/story/28-years-later-danny-boyles-new-zombie-flick-was-shot-on-an-iphone-15/">Wired</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280444" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/6beastgripdofadapter-531x580.jpeg" alt="" width="531" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/6beastgripdofadapter-531x580.jpeg 531w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/6beastgripdofadapter.jpeg 825w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 531px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲配合外置配件可安装镜头至 iPhone 上，另外亦可将 iPhone 安装在脚架上，图片来源：<a href="https://www.wired.com/story/28-years-later-danny-boyles-new-zombie-flick-was-shot-on-an-iphone-15/">Wired</a></p><p>故事背景设定在病毒爆发 28 年（ 10,228 日）后，社会濒临崩溃，秩序荡然无存。幸存者于孤岛寻找避难之所，然而危机四伏，生机渺茫。导演 Danny Boyle 再度执导，演员阵容包括 Jodie Comer、 Aaron Taylor-Johnson 和 Ralph Fiennes。此外，有传闻 Cillian Murphy 可能以丧尸形象回归，惟未获官方确认。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280446" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/28yearslaterofficial-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/28yearslaterofficial-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/28yearslaterofficial.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲有传，净系睇咗 Trailier 已经觉得好期待，其中一幕有只丧尸个轮廓有啲似 Cillian Murphy，唔知系咪真系佢嚟😏😏 将以丧尸形象回归，图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mcvLKldPM08">Sony Pictures Entertainment</a></p><p>严格来说，《28 Years Later》并非首部使用 iPhone 拍摄的电影，早在 2015 年 Sean Baker 已开始使用 iPhone 5S 拍摄《Tangerine》，其后 Steven Soderbergh 亦在 2018 年使用 iPhone 7Plus 拍摄《Unsane》，惟上面的电影均是限量发行的低成本艺术电影。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280447" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/tangerinesquare-694x463.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/tangerinesquare-694x463.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/tangerinesquare.jpeg 900w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Sean Baker 在 2015 年使用 iPhone 5S 拍摄《Tangerine》，图片来源：<a href="https://www.editmate.com/tangerine/">EditMate</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280448" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/64pjkdi5u5juevkv5rmg-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/64pjkdi5u5juevkv5rmg-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/64pjkdi5u5juevkv5rmg.jpg 800w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Steven Soderbergh 在 2018 年使用 iPhone 7 Plus 拍摄《Unsane》，图片来源：The National News</p><p>作为 2002 年经典恐怖片《28 Days Later》的续集，《28 Years Later》延续了前作的末日惊悚风格。预告片现已于 YouTube 发布。《28 Years Later》是新三部曲的第一部；即将上映的三部丧尸电影均由《28 Days Later》 原编剧 Alex Garland 编写剧本。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://9to5mac.com/2024/12/10/iphone-15-28-years-later-trailer/">9to5Mac</a>、<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mcvLKldPM08">Sony Picture Entertainment@YouTube</a>、<a href="https://www.bosshunting.com.au/entertainment/movies/28-years-later-trailer/">Boss Hunting</a></p><p>====== 加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事 ========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
